Voicesmith
==========

REQUIREMENTS:

* Oracle JDK 6 (usually 32-bit)
* Android SDK (API Level 8)
* Android NDK

DEPENDENCIES:

* Kiss FFT (Mark Borgerding) -- already included
* GreenDroid (Cyril Mottier) -- download separately
* GreenDroid/GDPreferenceActivity (Julien Dupouy) -- paste above

HOW TO BUILD:

Voicesmith repository contains Eclipse project files, an auto-generated Ant build script and a custom Makefile to handle the JNI source code.

Feel free to setup an IDE of your choise, e.g. Eclipse. But don't forget to download all dependencies and reference them in your project.